These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, 7up, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, skydiving, filmmaking
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking iced-tea##7
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta       | sprite | iced-tea        |
| Hobby      | skydiving  | magic-tricks | filmmaking        | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, turtle, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, skiing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | turtle | pony       | fish         | cat     |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | water-polo | skiing | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, drama, thriller, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, rock, disco, r&b
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of rock and the fan of salsa##7
3. the fan of disco is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the person watching drama movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | time-travel | thriller | horror  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | salsa  | r&b   | rock |

