.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, video-games, filmmaking, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, parkour, cricket, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | puzzles | rock-climbing       | filmmaking |
| Sport   | parkour      | basketball   | cricket | soccer  |

