.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, gardening, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, russian, pakistani
1. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
2. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the pakistani is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is baking##7
5. the pakistani is on the left of the russian##1
6. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening | baking   | puzzles | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | spanish      | nigerian | pakistani      | russian |

