.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, fanta, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, thai, australian, german
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the australian##1
2. the australian is the person drinking juice##1
3. the thai is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the german##3
6. the german is somewhere between the pakistani and the thai##7
7. the australian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | milk      | fanta | juice     |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | german | thai   | australian |

