.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, corn, papaya, zucchini
There are 4 different nationalities: french, japanese, italian, canadian
1. the french is on the far left##1
2. the person eating corn is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
4. the canadian is somewhere between the person eating apple and the person eating papaya##7
5. the italian is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
6. the canadian is on the left or right of the italian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | zucchini    | apple   | corn | papaya  |
| Nationality   | french | italian | canadian    | japanese |

