.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, russian, thai
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, mouse, frog
1. the indonesian is not the owner of the frog##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
3. the thai is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the russian is somewhere between the thai and the french##7
5. the indonesian is on the left of the french##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | thai | russian | indonesian | french |
| Pet           | mouse   | frog    | rat       | snake  |

