.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, lawyer, pilot, journalist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, soul, indie
1. the teacher is not the fan of ambient##6
2. the pilot is on the right of the teacher##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the fan of indie##1
5. the pilot is somewhere between the fan of indie and the lawyer##7
6. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | journalist | teacher | pilot | lawyer |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | soul      | ambient | d&b            |

