2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching horror movies and the fan of jazz##2
6. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
