4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is singing##7

