2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person driving the helicopter##6
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person who's hobby is photography##7
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | gardening | magic-tricks | woodworking | photography |
| Transport   | tram   | snowmobile      | helicopter        | motorbike  |

