.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, ambient, techno, trance
1. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
2. the fan of trance is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of techno##7
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | juice   | milk | sprite | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | techno   | trance | ambient |

