3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
6. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
