.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, cat, bird, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, helicopter, roller, airplane
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person driving the train and the owner of the cat##7
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
5. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | cat    | bird | rabbit     | goat |
| Transport   | roller | airplane  | helicopter | train |

 